## Ingredients

- 1 tbsp olive oil
- 1/4 cup chopped onion
- 2 cloves garlic, crushed
- 1 tsp cumin
- 2 15 oz cans black beans (drained and rinsed)
- 1 8 oz can tomato sauce
- 1/4 cup vegetable broth
- 1/2 tsp salt
- 2 tbsp cilantro

## Instructions

1. Heat oil
2. Saute onions until translucent
3. Add garlic and cumin and cook additional 30 second
4. Add beans, sauce, broth, salt
5. Simmer 10-15 minutes

